Fair Use:
I am using this music under the principles of fair use as it enhances the educational nature of my Python tutorial videos. The music serves as background ambiance with a lower volume, creating a more engaging and enjoyable viewing experience for learners. Importantly, the music does not constitute the primary content of the video, but rather acts as a supplementary element to maintain viewer interest.

The purpose of utilizing this music is solely educational, aiming to enhance the instructional value of the tutorial without distracting viewers from the main content. Furthermore, the portion of the music used is limited and does not constitute a substantial part of the overall video.

This use adheres to the fair use doctrine, as it aligns with the principles of criticism, comment, news reporting, teaching, scholarship, and research.
